column5: Just excited to be legal now is all!! haha good luck out there guys  Hawk
Happy B day man thats a big step I got in LOTS of trouble back in that area of my life ,have a good one
Happy B-Day! Now you can have your first beer
I have tackle in my box that is older than you! Many happy returns of the day!
Beeeer..  Nectar of the Gods.  It tastes soo much better when it's legal, or at the rippers..  Happy Birthday!!  HD
She-it Roy and I have tackle that is older than most of your fathers... And it still catches fish!
Wow!  You have your whole life ahead of you. Proceed with restraint.  Try to begin saving 10-20% of your income, instead of blowing it.
Happy Birthday!  ohhhh to be 19 again!!

Hope you had a great day celebrating your new "Legal status" How's your head feeling this morning?  I'll bet this first 19 years went real sllloooooowwwww....But don't worry, the next 19 will go twice as fast!
Happy B-Day! Ahh, to be young again. Enjoy it man!! It's all down hill from here.  :lol:
Happy belated to ya Bud. At 19 you have a real good chance of doing a whole lot of great things in your life. Go for it!
